      },
      "time": "~20s",
      "narrative": "- Tune starts from what we learned in Observe.\n- Performance is visible.\n- Cost is visible.\n- Now we use that information to make the system better.",
      "demo_actions": "Open the optimization area in Foundry and frame the goal as better quality at lower cost.",
      "screenshot": null
